 project! Essential Job functions and responsibilities: Participate in group and individual interviews, presentations, and trainings to gauge client's pain points Develop strong relationships with both clients and the innovation labs programming team Conduct research to understand emerging technologies and help determine the viability of future projects Assess market interest in potential solutions through customer development Participate in project design sessions utilizing scrum and lean startup methodologies About Vertex We have enjoyed workplace and business recognitions including Philly.com's Top Places to Work for three years in a row, Working Mother 100 Best Companies, and SmartCEO's Philadelphia Corporate Culture Award. Known for our innovative culture, Vertex is a privately held company that employs over 850 professionals across the globe, at its headquarters in the U.S. (King of Prussia, PA) and offices in Europe (London), Brazil (So Paulo), Naperville, IL, and Sarasota, FL. Learn more about our company, philosophy, philanthropy and values on our website, www.vertexinc.com/our-company and watch our latest video HERE. "
